  <title translate="true">Функции malloc() и free()</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para style="margin-bottom:2px; margin-left:4px;"><anchor id="hdr" styleclass="Heading1"></anchor><text style="font-family:Verdana; font-size:10pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;" translate="true">Функции malloc() и free()</text></para>
