    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:79px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">необходимо подключить</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">#include</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#a31515;" translate="true">&lt;cstdlib&gt;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">?</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">Функция malloc выделяет динамически память а</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">функция free освобождает ее.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">malloc возвращает указатель типа </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">void</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> на начало выделенной памяти</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">Если malloc вернула 0 то не удалось выделить память по каким то причинам</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">malloc(size_t количество БАЙТ) параметр необходимое количество байт</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> s[300]; </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">// Массив из 300 элементов типа int (напомню имя массива есть указатель)</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> *p; </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">// Указатель типа int</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> *d; </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">// Указатель типа int</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> main(){</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;p = (</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">*) malloc(100); </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Выделии 100 байт памяти (указатель *P c базовым типом</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">// </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">int хранит адрес первого элемента)</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;d = (</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">*) malloc(</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">sizeof</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">(</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">) * 100); </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Выделили память для 100 элементов типа int</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">// </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">(Самый правильный способ)(машинонезависимый)</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;free(d);</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Освободит память 100 элементов int выделенную выше</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;p = s;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Присвоили указателю адрес постоянного массива</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">// </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#ff0000;" translate="true">(!ПРИ ЭТОМ ПАМЯТЬ ВЫДЕЛЕННАЯ ВЫШЕ НЕОСВОБОЖДЕНА</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">)</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;free(p);</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Ошибка так как *p указывает на постоянный массив</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;free(s);</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Ошибка так как s это массив (постоянный)</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> v[3];</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Локальный массив</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;free (v);</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Ошибка</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Еще</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> *m;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Указатель</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> *x;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Указатель</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;m = (</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">*) malloc(</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">sizeof</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">(</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">int</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">) * 10);</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Выделить память для 10 элементов int</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;x = m;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Сохраним указатель еще раз</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;*(m+3) = 11; </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">// Использование адресной арифметики (правильный подход) к использованию</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;// &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160; динамической памяти</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;m++; </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">// Изменяем адрес</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;*m = 43; </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Записываем во вторую ячейку значение</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;//free(m);//Ошибка так как адрес изменен</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; &#160;free(x);</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">//Освобождаем память</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#008000;" translate="true">?</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> &#160; </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#0000ff;" translate="true">return</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true"> 0;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-left:136px; line-height:1.0; page-break-after:auto; tabstops:none;"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Consolas; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:baseline; color:#000000;" translate="true">}</text></para>
